The paper deals with recommender systems, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper proposes a neural model that uses unstructured text data, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL). The model also involves transfer learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.DL.
